  "title": "Business Project Manager",
  "description": "<p>Lead and drive new business development in the Singapore market</p><p>·       Identify, pursue, and close high-value opportunities across Medical, Aerospace and MNC</p><p>·       Develop sales strategies, market entry plans, investment plans, and business proposals to grow revenue and market share</p><p>·       Prepare investment proposals supported by market analysis, customer demand, and commercial justification</p><p>·       Conduct market and industry analysis and translate insights into clear business plans and execution actions</p><p>·       Achieve revenue targets and strategic KPIs</p><p>·       Build and manage strong relationships with customers and stakeholders</p><p>·       Collaborate closely with internal teams to execute growth and investment initiatives</p><p>·       Attend industry and networking events to expand market presence</p><p>·       Track pipeline, forecasts, and performance, and present structured reports to management</p><p>·       Ensure accurate and timely CRM updates for all leads, opportunities, and quotations</p><p>·       Communicate clearly and professionally to align teams, drive decisions, and deliver results</p>",
